<%= section "Overview of topics" do %>

In OST, the topics section is where you add course materials, including exercises and resources.<p>
   
  <p>A topic can be understood in 2 ways: </p>   
    (a) <strong>a topic is a group of related exercises and resources</strong>; and <br/>
    (b) <strong>a topic is a building block of an assignment</strong>. <br/>

<% end %>

